text: Sebastes ventricosus, the Japanese black seaperch, or Japanese Blueback Seaperch is a species of fish in the rockfish family found in the Northwest Pacific. ==See also== *Sebastes inermis *Sebastes cheni == References == ==External links== * * Japanese black seaperch Category:Fish of Japan Category:Endemic fauna of Japan Japanese black seaperch
title: Sebastes ventricosus
